<reference id="choices" xml:lang="en-us">
   <title>
      <keyword>choices</keyword>
   </title>
   <shortdesc>The &lt;<keyword>choices</keyword>&gt; element contains a list of &lt;<keyword>choice</keyword>&gt; elements.
It is used when the user will need to choose one of several actions while
performing the steps of a task. </shortdesc>
   <prolog>
      <metadata>
         <keywords>
            <indexterm>choices</indexterm>
            <indexterm>Task
elements<indexterm>choices</indexterm>
