      </section>
      <example>
         <codeblock>&lt;step&gt;&lt;cmd&gt;Choose a server.&lt;/cmd&gt;
&lt;choices&gt;&lt;choice&gt;If you have a remote server you want to test on, type the
IP address or hostname of the server here.&lt;/choice&gt;
&lt;choice&gt;If you want to do local testing, just type localhost.&lt;/choice&gt;
&lt;/choices&gt;
&lt;/step&gt;</codeblock>
